<section id='ChangeMenuStyle'>
<title>ChangeMenuStyle</title>

<cmdsynopsis>
	<command>ChangeMenuStyle</command>
	<arg choice='plain'
		><replaceable>menustyle</replaceable
	></arg>
	<arg choice='plain' rep='repeat'
		><replaceable>menu</replaceable
	></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>

<para>Changes the menu style of
<replaceable>menu</replaceable> to <replaceable>menustyle</replaceable>.
You may specify more than one menu in each call of
<emphasis remap='B'>ChangeMenuStyle</emphasis>.</para>

</section>
